data.description: Welcome home to 1331 Forrest in Metamora! This beautiful 2 story 4 bed 3.5 bath home sits on nearly half an acre in highly sought after Metamora! Major updates done throughout including new roof in 2020, HVAC in 2023, Windows and doors in 2023, New deck in 2022, as well as a whole house water filtration system! Quiet street makes this location a park like setting! Two living rooms make this home the perfect place to entertain! The interior has hardwood floors throughout the main level and the upper level. The basement is a walk out basement that leads you to the patio and into the gorgeous back yard! Don't miss your opportunity, call to schedule your showing today!
